# Toolchain

## Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Dev server | `npm run dev` |
| Build | `npm run build` |
| Preview | `npm run preview` |
| Check (format + lint + types) | `vp check` |
| Fix (format + lint) | `vp check --fix` |
| Unit tests | `vp test` |
| E2E tests | `npm run test:e2e` |
| Render diagrams | `npm run diagrams` |
| Validate (config + cross-refs) | `npm run validate` |
| Validate content (`@pagesmith/site` validators) | `npm run validate:content` |
| Validate diagrams (`diagramkit validate`) | `npm run validate:diagrams` |
| Validate everything (content + diagrams + build + cross-refs) | `npm run validate:all` / `npm run validate:full` |
| Validate dist | `npm run validate:dist` |

## Tech Stack

- Runtime: Node.js 24 (LTS), managed by Vite+
- Script runner: tsx (TypeScript execution)
- Bundler: esbuild (runtime JS)
- Toolchain: Vite+ (`vp check`, `vp test`)
- Content: `@pagesmith/core` (collections, markdown, validators) + `@pagesmith/site` (JSX runtime, CSS, runtime JS, SSG, build/content validators)
- Diagrams: `diagramkit` (Mermaid, Excalidraw, Draw.io, Graphviz)
- JSX: `@pagesmith/site` server runtime (no React) — `jsxImportSource: "@pagesmith/site"`
- CSS: lightningcss via `@pagesmith/site`, light/dark via CSS variables
- Testing: Vitest (unit) + Playwright (E2E)
- CI/CD: GitHub Pages via `.github/workflows/gh-pages.yml`

## Style

- No semicolons (ASI)
- Single quotes for TS, double quotes for JSX
- Trailing commas
- 2-space indent
- Always parenthesise arrow function params

See `.prettierrc.json` for formatting config.
